&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the fix &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kevin.cyj&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kevin.cyj&quot;&gt;kevin.cyj&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=siddheshghadi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;siddheshghadi&quot;&gt;siddheshghadi&lt;/a&gt; for reporting the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
